85fc78bfa83db\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nEste m\u00f3dulo permite a exporta\u00e7\u00e3o dos documentos fiscais por per\u00edodo.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nAbra o menu Fiscal>Contador>Fechamento Fiscal e defina as exporta\u00e7\u00f5es de documentos fiscais por per\u00edodo.\n\nObs. No caso de documentos emitidos pelos parceiros, os arquivos exportados ser\u00e3o aqueles que est\u00e3o como anexo do documento fiscal.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_br_fiscal_closing%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- KMEE\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [KMEE](https://www.kmee.com.br):\n\n  - Luis Felipe Mileo \\<<mailto:mileo@kmee.com.br>>\n  - Luis Otavio Malta Concei\u00e7\u00e3o \\<<mailto:luis.malta@kmee.com.br>>\n\n- [Akretion](https://www.akretion.com/pt-BR):\n\n  - Renato Lima \\<<mailto:renato.lima@akretion.com.br>>\n\n- [Escodoo](https://www.escodoo.com.br):\n\n  - Marcel Savegnago \\<<mailto:marcel.savegnago@escodoo.com.br>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-brazil](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/tree/14.0/l10n_br_fiscal_closing) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models.closing", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models..closing", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models.document", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models..document", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models.document", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 KMEE INFORMATICA LTDA", "Gabriel Cardoso de Faria <gabriel.cardoso@kmee.com.br>"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models.document.FiscalDocument", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models.document.FiscalDocument._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models.document.FiscalDocument.close_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.tests.test_fiscal_closing", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.tests..test_fiscal_closing", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.models", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing..models", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_fiscal_closing.__manifest_